Class NodesChanged

java.lang.Object
com.google.flatbuffers.Table
mobsya.fb.NodesChanged
public final class NodesChanged extends com.google.flatbuffers.Table
Message sent by the server when a node changes status. This messages is automatically sent when the application first connects and each time one or more node change status
